Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.29,0:00:08.93,Default,,0,0,0,,OK. Library... library... Where\Ndid they put the library?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.29,0:00:17.50,Default,,0,0,0,,This Castle looked a lot\Nsmaller from the outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.52,0:00:22.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Morning, Starlight.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.88,0:00:23.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoops!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.86,0:00:27.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, Spike! I guess I'm still\Ntrying to find my way around.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.02,0:00:30.60,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't happen to know\Nwhere the library is, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.19,0:00:32.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Next door on the left.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.76,0:00:35.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh. Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.07,0:00:39.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Acceptance, mm-hmm,\NAltruism, definitely.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.93,0:00:41.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Starlight! Good\Nmorning! Come in!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.15,0:00:44.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry I'm late. I got\Na little turned around.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.92,0:00:47.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I still can't believe you're\Nletting me stay here.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.84,0:00:51.03,Default,,0,0,0,,As your pupil. After\Neverything I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.12,0:00:55.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I'm not one to dwell on\Nthe past and neither should you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.38,0:00:59.08,Default,,0,0,0,,The castle is your home now and\Nas far as being my pupil goes...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.26,0:01:00.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I was just trying to figure out
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.57,0:01:02.41,Default,,0,0,0,,what your first friendship\Nlesson should be!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.63,0:01:05.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh. Well, it looks like you're\Nreally narrowing it down.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.68,0:01:09.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, these are just the As. After\Nthis, I move on to the Bs!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.41,0:01:25.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Regular subtitles\Nby YayPonies\NEat all muffins!\Nhttp://yayponies.eu/
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.79,0:01:55.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I know I'm just learning\Nabout friendship,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.64,0:01:58.72,Default,,0,0,0,,but I didn't think there were\Nthis many lessons for anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.00,0:02:00.31,Default,,0,0,0,,How do we choose?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.54,0:02:03.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe I should pare things down\Na bit before we go through them.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.15,0:02:05.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't you join the\Nothers in the throne room?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.04,0:02:07.92,Default,,0,0,0,,They're planning our trip\Nto the Crystal Empire
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.93,0:02:10.76,Default,,0,0,0,,when Shining Armor and Princess\NCadance have their baby.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.95,0:02:12.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Throne room. Got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.79,0:02:17.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, which way is\Nthe throne room?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.75,0:02:21.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I think we should leave ASAP!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.85,0:02:23.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to miss\Nthe Crystalling!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.69,0:02:26.53,Default,,0,0,0,,But, um, shouldn't we\Nwait for the invitation?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.89,0:02:29.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Frankly, I'm not exactly\Nclear on all the customs
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.43,0:02:31.24,Default,,0,0,0,,and traditions of\Nthe Crystal Empire.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.41,0:02:33.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Especially when it\Ncomes to a Crystalling.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.71,0:02:34.98,Default,,0,0,0,,What's a Crystalling?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.19,0:02:37.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, that's just\Nit, Darling.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.57,0:02:40.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Princess Cadance and Shining\NArmor's baby is due any day
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.87,0:02:42.43,Default,,0,0,0,,and we're still not sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.67,0:02:45.73,Default,,0,0,0,,The Crystal Empire was\Ngone for a thousand years.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.04,0:02:48.59,Default,,0,0,0,,A lot of their customs\Nare a bit murky.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.98,0:02:51.28,Default,,0,0,0,,We know it's got something\Nto do with the new baby.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.47,0:02:52.28,Default,,0,0,0,,And a party!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.77,0:02:53.91,Default,,0,0,0,,And the Crystal Heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.22,0:02:55.06,Default,,0,0,0,,And a party!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.25,0:02:57.21,Default,,0,0,0,,And some kind of cool energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.52,0:02:58.48,Default,,0,0,0,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.77,0:03:00.15,Default,,0,0,0,,A PARTY!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.60,0:03:04.47,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not hard\Nto understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.71,0:03:06.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Most things in the\NCrystal Empire aren't.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.99,0:03:11.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Like how I'm a big hero\Nthere, for example.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.55,0:03:18.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Plus, I've had to help Twilight
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.73,0:03:20.26,Default,,0,0,0,,do a lot of research\Non Crystallings.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.75,0:03:23.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Whenever a baby is born\Nin the Crystal Empire,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.10,0:03:26.18,Default,,0,0,0,,the parents bring it\Nbefore the Crystal Heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.70,0:03:29.05,Default,,0,0,0,,They get the purest shard\Nof crystal they can find,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.07,0:03:31.51,Default,,0,0,0,,then pick a Crystaller\Nto present the baby
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.53,0:03:33.14,Default,,0,0,0,,to everypony who comes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.52,0:03:36.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Then they all share the\Nlight and joy they feel,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.43,0:03:38.79,Default,,0,0,0,,feeding it into the crystal\Nthat joins with the Heart
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.97,0:03:40.61,Default,,0,0,0,,and increases its power.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.64,0:03:43.60,Default,,0,0,0,,And this is going to\Nbe a Royal Crystalling,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.73,0:03:45.94,Default,,0,0,0,,so pretty much the whole\NEmpire will show up.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.17,0:03:47.97,Default,,0,0,0,,That hasn't happened\Nin a millennia.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.26,0:03:52.21,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean it increases\Nthe Crystal Heart's power?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.33,0:03:55.11,Default,,0,0,0,,The energy it uses to protect\Nthe Crystal Empire, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.30,0:03:56.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Protect it from what?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.10,0:03:59.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't help Twilight\Nwith that part.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.43,0:04:09.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Twilight, can\NI ask you something
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.63,0:04:10.74,Default,,0,0,0,,about the Crystal Empire?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.13,0:04:13.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha! Funny you\Nshould mention it...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.28,0:04:15.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Because I just narrowed your\Nfirst friendship lesson
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.35,0:04:16.38,Default,,0,0,0,,down to three options.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.65,0:04:18.67,Default,,0,0,0,,And one of them is in\Nthe Crystal Empire.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.82,0:04:19.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.62,0:04:22.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I found out that's\Nwhere the first pony
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.25,0:04:23.52,Default,,0,0,0,,you ever cared about lives!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.77,0:04:24.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Sunburst?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.14,0:04:26.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course that's just one idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.14,0:04:28.60,Default,,0,0,0,,We could also go to\NGriffinstone.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.63,0:04:31.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Making friends with a Griffin\Nis a challenge all by itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.77,0:04:33.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Or we could tag\Nalong with the CMCs
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.55,0:04:35.29,Default,,0,0,0,,the next time they help a\Npony who can't figure out
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.35,0:04:39.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Starlight, is something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.99,0:04:43.62,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Oh, no. Those\Nall sound great.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.76,0:04:45.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I know! I guess you\Nwere right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.65,0:04:47.58,Default,,0,0,0,,It is going to be\Nhard to choose one.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.95,0:04:50.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.57,0:05:06.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Ugh! I am never going to find\Nmy way around this place!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.56,0:05:09.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Gee, Starlight, what's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.39,0:05:10.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know, Spike.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.90,0:05:13.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Twilight's figuring out what\Nmy first friendship lesson is
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.63,0:05:17.06,Default,,0,0,0,,and I guess I'm not exactly\Nthrilled with the options.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.58,0:05:19.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, with one of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.01,0:05:20.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Which one?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.26,0:05:23.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Reuniting me with\Nmy first friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.53,0:05:26.16,Default,,0,0,0,,What's so terrible about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.21,0:05:32.45,Default,,0,0,0,,When we were foals,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.47,0:05:35.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Sunburst knew everything there\Nwas to know about magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.49,0:05:47.48,Default,,0,0,0,,He always knew just what to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.91,0:05:58.42,Default,,0,0,0,,And he was always\Nthere to help me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.70,0:06:11.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess it's not surprising that\NSunburst got his cutie mark
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.59,0:06:15.23,Default,,0,0,0,,in magic and went off to\NPrincess Celestia's school.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.72,0:06:17.17,Default,,0,0,0,,But when he left...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.74,0:06:19.64,Default,,0,0,0,,You blamed cutie marks and\Nstripped a whole village
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.66,0:06:21.25,Default,,0,0,0,,of theirs and when Twilight\Nand the others stopped you,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.27,0:06:23.34,Default,,0,0,0,,you went back in time and\Nalmost destroyed Equestria.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.16,0:06:28.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Not really stuff I'm super\Neager to tell Sunburst about.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.58,0:06:32.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, he's probably some\Nbig, important wizard now
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.25,0:06:36.01,Default,,0,0,0,,and I can't even find my way\Naround Twilight's Castle.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.29,0:06:38.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, if Sunburst is\Nthat good at magic,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.88,0:06:42.04,Default,,0,0,0,,maybe he'd appreciate\Nyour exploits.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.45,0:06:45.30,Default,,0,0,0,,You should talk to\NTwilight about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.51,0:06:47.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure she'd want to\Nhear what you have to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.91,0:06:51.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I know, but I don't want her to\Nthink I'm not ready to learn
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.82,0:06:54.54,Default,,0,0,0,,or that I'm not grateful\Nfor everything she's doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.70,0:06:56.36,Default,,0,0,0,,SPIKE! COME QUICK!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.16,0:07:08.91,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a Crystalling invitation!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.10,0:07:12.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Shining Armor's a\Nfather! I'm an Aunt!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.28,0:07:14.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, this settles it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.79,0:07:16.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Since we're going to\Nthe Crystal Empire,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.63,0:07:18.89,Default,,0,0,0,,your first friendship\Nlesson is going to be
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.37,0:07:21.35,Default,,0,0,0,,reuniting with Sunburst!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.48,0:07:23.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Great.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.69,0:07:44.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, Applejack, what is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.74,0:07:46.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, just a little\Nsomething for the young'un.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.21,0:07:51.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Made from genuine Sweet\NApple Acres apple trees.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.63,0:07:52.97,Default,,0,0,0,,We make 'em for all the Apples
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.19,0:07:56.34,Default,,0,0,0,,and anypony related to Twilight\Nis practically family.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.48,0:08:03.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. It's OK, but it's no\NCloudsdale Mobile...BAM!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.88,0:08:06.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Oooh! Pretty!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.25,0:08:10.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, a mobile is real nice...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.88,0:08:14.01,Default,,0,0,0,,as long as you have something to\Nlay in so you can look at it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.29,0:08:17.15,Default,,0,0,0,,And a fetching blanket\Nto keep you warm.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.10,0:08:20.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure Shining Armor\Nand Princess Cadance
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.14,0:08:22.90,Default,,0,0,0,,will love all our gifts, but\NI think they're more happy
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.91,0:08:24.89,Default,,0,0,0,,we'll be attending the\Nbaby's Crystalling.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.11,0:08:27.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Ooh! I can't wait to see\Nall that light and love
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.58,0:08:30.51,Default,,0,0,0,,make the Crystal Heart even\Nmore sparkly and shiny!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.75,0:08:32.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, Pinkie,\Nthe Crystal Heart
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.70,0:08:34.66,Default,,0,0,0,,is an ancient and\Npowerful relic.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.72,0:08:37.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Without its magic, the\NCrystal Empire would be lost
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.02,0:08:37.99,Default,,0,0,0,,to the Frozen North.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.30,0:08:42.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow. This Crystalling\Nsounds pretty important.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.71,0:08:45.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd understand if you\Nwanted to, you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.05,0:08:48.68,Default,,0,0,0,,wait to do a different\Nfriendship lesson
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.70,0:08:49.85,Default,,0,0,0,,when we get back.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.22,0:08:52.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you kidding?\NThis trip is perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.69,0:08:55.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Not only do I get to see the\Nbaby and take part in a ceremony
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.72,0:08:57.89,Default,,0,0,0,,that helps maintain the\Nmagic of the Crystal Empire,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.10,0:08:59.87,Default,,0,0,0,,but I'm starting\Nmy new pupil off
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.90,0:09:03.59,Default,,0,0,0,,with the most amazing friendship\Nlesson ever. I can't wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.87,0:09:07.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Right. Me neither.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.08,0:09:14.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, Twilight,\NI am a little worried
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.30,0:09:15.76,Default,,0,0,0,,about meeting Sunburst.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.32,0:09:19.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, trust me, I know what\Nit's like to see old friends,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.48,0:09:21.36,Default,,0,0,0,,but I'll be right there\Nto help things along.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.56,0:09:24.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I've broken the whole lesson\Ndown into a few easy steps
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.15,0:09:26.71,Default,,0,0,0,,to ensure this reunion\Ngoes off without a hitch.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.92,0:09:37.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Step one, head to Sunburst's\Nhouse and get you two started
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.75,0:09:38.77,Default,,0,0,0,,on the right hoof.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.93,0:09:42.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Step two, get to the Castle with\Nenough time to visit the baby.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.00,0:09:44.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Shining Armor!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.88,0:09:46.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Twilight!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.00,0:09:48.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't know you\Nwere meeting us.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.97,0:09:52.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course I am. It's me.\NRight here. Here I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.59,0:09:54.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Why wouldn't I come\Nmeet my sister?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.76,0:09:56.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Though we have met before.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.46,0:09:58.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.78,0:10:02.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Never better! Being a father\Nis amazing and wonderful
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.12,0:10:05.38,Default,,0,0,0,,and amazing and\Nconfusing and amazing...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.46,0:10:07.26,Default,,0,0,0,,But surprising too, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.59,0:10:11.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, not that you'd know. You\Nwouldn't know, I know. You know?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.12,0:10:16.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry. I haven't really slept\Nsince Cadence had the baby.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.10,0:10:19.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Come to think of it,\Nshe hasn't either.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.04,0:10:21.86,Default,,0,0,0,,It sure would be\Ngreat to get a break.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.20,0:10:25.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh. Of course. I don't\Nknow what I was thinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.80,0:10:27.74,Default,,0,0,0,,You two probably need\Nall kinds of help!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.14,0:10:30.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, Starlight,\Nbut I guess combining
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.61,0:10:33.50,Default,,0,0,0,,your first lesson with this\Nvisit wasn't such a good idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.95,0:10:37.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, don't be ridiculous!\NYou're an aunt now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.04,0:10:41.90,Default,,0,0,0,,That's way more important\Nthan some friendship lesson.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.56,0:10:44.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I just wish there\Nwas a way to do both.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.18,0:10:48.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe there is.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.57,0:10:50.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You've already done the\Nwork for Starlight's lesson
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.39,0:10:51.31,Default,,0,0,0,,with this list.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.51,0:10:53.12,Default,,0,0,0,,All we have to do is follow it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.02,0:10:56.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Spike, you're a genius!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.44,0:10:59.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. Genius.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.01,0:11:00.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Then it's settled.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.98,0:11:03.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Shining Armor and I will\Nhead straight to the castle
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.47,0:11:05.58,Default,,0,0,0,,and you two can head\Nstraight to Sunburst's.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.79,0:11:06.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Aye, aye, princess.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.15,0:11:12.61,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, big brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.84,0:11:15.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go see this\Namazing baby pony.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.11,0:11:24.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I know you're a little\Nworried about this reunion,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.30,0:11:26.61,Default,,0,0,0,,but I'm sure Twilight's\Ngot everything covered.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.08,0:11:30.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything except how I'd rather\Ndo absolutely anything else.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.49,0:11:33.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I bet she's taken\Nthat into account too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.75,0:11:37.78,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all part of the\Nlesson. Trust the lesson.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.14,0:11:39.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.13,0:11:45.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, is that you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.10,0:11:48.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh. Yep. It sure is.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.85,0:11:51.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Now... according to the\Nlist, Sunburst's house is--
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.67,0:11:54.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Why is there a statue of\Nyou in the Crystal Empire?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.86,0:11:57.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Because Spike, the\Nbrave and glorious,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.35,0:11:59.57,Default,,0,0,0,,saved all of us\Nfrom King Sombra.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.80,0:12:02.25,Default,,0,0,0,,And then again during\Nthe Equestria Games.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.42,0:12:03.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.41,0:12:05.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Really! Big fan.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.24,0:12:08.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, when were you going\Nto tell me about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.24,0:12:11.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's no big deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.50,0:12:13.69,Default,,0,0,0,,IT MOST CERTAINLY IS!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.02,0:12:16.07,Default,,0,0,0,,That's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.58,0:12:19.75,Default,,0,0,0,,We're not going anywhere\Nuntil I get the whole story.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.70,0:12:28.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Before we go in, I should\Nprobably tell you,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.81,0:12:31.83,Default,,0,0,0,,seeing the baby might\Nbe a bit of a shock.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.15,0:12:34.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, big brother,\NI've met babies before.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.10,0:12:37.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I expect meeting this one\Nwon't be any different.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.47,0:12:47.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course, I could be wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.91,0:12:55.83,Default,,0,0,0,,iiiiiaaa, ahhh, GNAGRN
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.88,0:12:57.21,Default,,0,0,0,,The baby is an Alicorn?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.05,0:12:59.99,Default,,0,0,0,,It looks that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.07,0:13:00.70,Default,,0,0,0,,But! but!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.05,0:13:03.15,Default,,0,0,0,,But I thought Alicorn\Nwings had to be earned
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.18,0:13:06.44,Default,,0,0,0,,by accomplishing some great\Nprincess-worthy deed.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.68,0:13:09.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, how can you just\Nbe born with them?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.48,0:13:10.77,Default,,0,0,0,,The birth of an Alicorn
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.79,0:13:13.22,Default,,0,0,0,,is something Equestria\Nhas never seen.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.51,0:13:15.82,Default,,0,0,0,,It is beyond even\Nour understanding.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.20,0:13:18.19,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not very reassuring.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.41,0:13:20.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, a unicorn and a Pegasus!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.76,0:13:24.74,Default,,0,0,0,,So, she could be a super strong\Nflyer and have crazy baby magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.31,0:13:28.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I know all about\Nsuper strong flying.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.40,0:13:30.48,Default,,0,0,0,,And I can help keep\Ntabs on her magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.57,0:13:46.02,Default,,0,0,0,,It appears her magic\Nis more powerful
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.04,0:13:47.81,Default,,0,0,0,,than that of a newborn unicorn.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.99,0:13:49.97,Default,,0,0,0,,The crowds have already\Nstarted to gather.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.47,0:13:55.10,Default,,0,0,0,,This Crystalling is\Ngonna be some party!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.85,0:13:59.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you think we\Nshould call it off?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.39,0:14:03.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, we've all faced a lot\Nworse than baby magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.65,0:14:04.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't imagine cancelling
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.92,0:14:06.87,Default,,0,0,0,,such a beautiful and\Nimportant ceremony
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.09,0:14:09.55,Default,,0,0,0,,over something so\Npotentially adorable.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.62,0:14:12.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah! Of course! Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.50,0:14:14.57,Default,,0,0,0,,In light of the little\None's abilities,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.70,0:14:17.41,Default,,0,0,0,,this Crystalling might be\Nmore important than ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.92,0:14:19.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Perhaps you should\Naddress your subjects
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.78,0:14:21.02,Default,,0,0,0,,and remind them of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.98,0:14:32.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Shining Armor, do you\Nhave everything you need
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.04,0:14:32.98,Default,,0,0,0,,for the ceremony?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.91,0:14:37.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Oh! NO! I still have to\Ninterview the Honor Guards,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.94,0:14:40.61,Default,,0,0,0,,chose the Purity Crystal\Nand pick a Crystaller!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.43,0:14:44.04,Default,,0,0,0,,All right. Take it easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.25,0:14:46.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Pinkie can stay here with me\Nand keep an eye on the baby.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.76,0:14:51.75,Default,,0,0,0,,And we'll all help you\Nwith everything else.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.96,0:14:58.63,Default,,0,0,0,,That is if you can stay awake\Nlong enough to tell us how.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.26,0:15:01.91,Default,,0,0,0,,And that's how we found\Nthe Crystal Heart,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.05,0:15:04.78,Default,,0,0,0,,defeated King Sombra\Nand saved the Empire.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.94,0:15:07.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Yay! We love you, Spike! Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.02,0:15:10.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell the one about\Nthe Equestria Games!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.89,0:15:14.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, as much as I love\Nreliving my heroic deeds,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.55,0:15:16.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Starlight and I have an\Nimportant lesson to do
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.86,0:15:18.90,Default,,0,0,0,,by order of the\NPrincess of Friendship.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.13,0:15:20.64,Default,,0,0,0,,AWWWWW!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.93,0:15:24.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, come on, Spike. I want to\Nhear about the Games, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.66,0:15:27.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I know you're nervous\Nabout seeing Sunburst,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.85,0:15:29.68,Default,,0,0,0,,but it says right\Nin step three to,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.09,0:15:33.51,Default,,0,0,0,,"deal with your fears by facing\Nthem," not by putting it off.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.82,0:15:37.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Ugh. Let's go get\Nthis over with.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.26,0:15:45.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.42,0:15:46.05,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.28,0:15:48.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Knocking on the door isn't\Nthe next thing on the list.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.92,0:15:49.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.22,0:15:52.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I know Twilight can\Nbe a little nitpicky,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.26,0:15:54.05,Default,,0,0,0,,but this is your first\Nlesson as her pupil
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.18,0:15:56.06,Default,,0,0,0,,and it's important\Nthat we do it right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.18,0:16:00.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine. What's the next\Nthing on the list?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.36,0:16:04.36,Default,,0,0,0,,"Before they see each other,\Nmake sure to highlight
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.39,0:16:05.83,Default,,0,0,0,,the importance of the meeting."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.12,0:16:08.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm pretty sure\Nwe can skip that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.69,0:16:09.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.93,0:16:12.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, if we skip it, the\Nwhole lesson could go south.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.43,0:16:14.49,Default,,0,0,0,,And then you might end up\Ntaking a giant step backwards
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.50,0:16:15.51,Default,,0,0,0,,instead of forwards.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.74,0:16:17.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe you'll never be\Nable to learn anything
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.27,0:16:18.51,Default,,0,0,0,,about friendship at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.46,0:16:22.67,Default,,0,0,0,,It's almost like your whole\Nfuture depends on this moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.07,0:16:26.40,Default,,0,0,0,,"Highlight the importance\Nof the meeting." Check.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.78,0:16:28.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe you\Nwanted to skip that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.29,0:16:43.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Sunburst?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.07,0:16:46.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes? What can I do for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.39,0:16:49.63,Default,,0,0,0,,It's, it's me. Starlight.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.94,0:16:52.06,Default,,0,0,0,,We used to be friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.94,0:16:59.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, of course! Starlight. My\Ngoodness, it's been a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.69,0:17:01.99,Default,,0,0,0,,What, what have\Nyou been up to?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.42,0:17:07.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Me? Oh, you know, some\Nof this, some of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.06,0:17:10.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Different stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.64,0:17:13.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Right now I'm sort of,\NTwilight Sparkle's new pupil.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.01,0:17:16.01,Default,,0,0,0,,The Princess of Friendship?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.38,0:17:20.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Heh. Yeah. That's actually\Nkind of why I'm here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.82,0:17:23.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, I know you're\Nprobably very busy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.96,0:17:24.86,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.49,0:17:27.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I figured\Nafter Magic School,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.66,0:17:30.26,Default,,0,0,0,,you'd go on to do important\Nwizard work, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.84,0:17:35.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh. No. Yes. Oh yes, that's\Nme. Yep. Important wizard.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.88,0:17:39.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Really busy with lots of,\Nuh... wizarding stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.71,0:17:44.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, well Good to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.63,0:17:48.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh. Maybe we\Nshould have skipped
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.56,0:17:50.93,Default,,0,0,0,,"highlighting the importance\Nof the meeting" after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.59,0:17:53.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Well? I guess that's that!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.47,0:17:55.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Starlight, come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.59,0:17:57.94,Default,,0,0,0,,We have to at least explain\Nwhat Twilight wants!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.63,0:17:59.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Ugh.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.18,0:18:11.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Dearest Citizens, I am sure\Nyou are all just as thrilled
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.75,0:18:15.89,Default,,0,0,0,,and ready for this Crystalling\Nas myself and Shining Armor.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.08,0:18:23.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not ready!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.01,0:18:25.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Take it easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.27,0:18:28.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Just pick whoever looks the\Nmost like Honor Guard material.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.56,0:18:30.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Right. Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.22,0:18:35.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry;
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.58,0:18:38.73,Default,,0,0,0,,fatherhood is way more\Nstressful than I ever thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.92,0:18:40.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I can only imagine.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.02,0:18:43.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, I know choosing\Nthe crystal of purity
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.70,0:18:45.43,Default,,0,0,0,,is a very important decision,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.64,0:18:48.35,Default,,0,0,0,,so I have gone through the\Ntrouble of arranging them
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.38,0:18:52.02,Default,,0,0,0,,in order from incredibly\Npure to outrageously pure.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.46,0:18:56.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, Rarity? Don't they\Nall sort of look the same?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.23,0:18:58.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh well, to the\Nuntrained eye, perhaps.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.26,0:19:01.40,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think,\NShining Armor?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.56,0:19:04.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I DON'T KNOW!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.41,0:19:07.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope Twilight and Pinkie
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.97,0:19:09.79,Default,,0,0,0,,are having better\Nluck with the baby.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.38,0:19:14.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, at least she's having fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.86,0:19:24.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Pinkie, hold her still!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.52,0:19:27.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm trying!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.73,0:19:40.11,Default,,0,0,0,,So, the Princess of\NFriendship wants you and I
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.14,0:19:41.51,Default,,0,0,0,,to be friends again?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.67,0:19:45.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I know. Weird, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.15,0:19:47.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.45,0:19:50.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Did something happen to you\Nafter I left for Magic School?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.84,0:19:54.51,Default,,0,0,0,,What? No! I don't see what\Nthat has to do with anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.05,0:19:56.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Why would you even ask that?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.61,0:20:01.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, did something\Nhappen to you
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.91,0:20:03.73,Default,,0,0,0,,after you left for magic school?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.85,0:20:10.42,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Um. No. Like you said,\NI'm a important wizard.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.99,0:20:14.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure there's something\Non Twilight's list
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.70,0:20:15.62,Default,,0,0,0,,that can help here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.68,0:20:27.79,Default,,0,0,0,,OK. I chose the Honor Guard,\Npicked the Purity Crystal
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.84,0:20:30.76,Default,,0,0,0,,and I know exactly who I\Nwant to be our Crystaller.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.89,0:20:32.82,Default,,0,0,0,,So, all we need is...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.35,0:20:35.35,Default,,0,0,0,,The baby?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.56,0:20:37.60,Default,,0,0,0,,We're here!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.73,0:20:41.36,Default,,0,0,0,,She's a really strong flyer!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.62,0:21:15.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm guessing that's gonna make\Nit hard to do the Crystalling.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.09,0:21:17.21,Default,,0,0,0,,It's worse than that...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.72,0:21:20.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Without the Heart, the Crystal\NEmpire is about to be buried
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.66,0:21:22.46,Default,,0,0,0,,under a mountain\Nof ice and snow!
